title: Wishbone Ash - Live Dates II - 1980 - Ltd. Edition - 320Kbps # D
description:
Wishbone Ash Mk. II 
Martin Turner, Andy Powell, Laurie Wisefield and Steve Upton

The long awaited second official Wishbone Ash live album and an excellent representation of the Mk.2 line-ups live capabilities. The first 25,000 copies of this album were a double with an extra free album included . . .
